org.eclipse.team.ui.synchronize

Class ParticipantSynchronizeWizard

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jface.wizard.Wizard
      • org.eclipse.team.ui.synchronize.ParticipantSynchronizeWizard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IWizard
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ModelParticipantWizard, SubscriberParticipantWizard

    public abstract class ParticipantSynchronizeWizard
extends Wizard
    This is a convenience class for creating wizards for use with the org.eclipse.team.ui.synchronizeWizard extension point.
    Since:
    3.2
